# SETUP.md - Installation Guide

## Prerequisites

- [Moltbot](https://github.com/moltbot/moltbot) installed
- Node.js 20+
- Anthropic API key

## Quick Start

### 1. Copy Workspace

```bash
# Copy this agent workspace to your Moltbot agents directory
cp -r {{AGENT_NAME}} ~/.moltbot/agents/
```

### 2. Configure Moltbot

Add the agent to your `moltbot.json`:

```json
{
  "agents": [
    {
      "id": "{{AGENT_NAME}}",
      "workspace": "~/.moltbot/agents/{{AGENT_NAME}}",
      "model": "claude-sonnet-4-20250514",
      "enabled": true
    }
  ]
}
```

